!&quot;<br>
I know I can't be the only one this is happening to.<br>
<br>
Who wants to do a charm quest?! I found information on three charms that I really like.  The first isn't the result of a quest, it's a drop in Hate's Fury.  And it makes me drool.<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=19994" target="top">Damn you plate classes!</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
Too bad I can't equip it.  I've never been to Hate's Fury, haven't done any research on the zone yet, but this would be such a nice item for the plate wearing jerks... I mean classes... in the guild or friends with the guild.<br>
<br>
The second charm that I like is the result of a quest.<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2320" target="top">Finally all my freaking dexterity is useful.</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
The quest doesn't seem too difficult.<br>
<br>
The third is the Emerald Warriors Charm, and also the result of a quest.<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2301" target="top">Oh Dadur!!!!!!!</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
Anything involving an NPC druid saying &quot;just let me die in peace!&quot; is sweet in my book.<br>
<br>
So, do any of these sound interesting/feasible to anyone else?  Or, perhaps you know of a more interesting charm quest?<br>
